  "text": "One can check that Λ is a Lagrangian submanifold of T * (B 3 × B 3 ), see also [CITATION_1] . Thanks to our assumption, the manifold has no conjugate points. The Lagrangian Λ away from the diagonal is the graph of the differential of the distance function i.e.",
